T1  - Attention: How high-frequency trading improves price efficiency following earnings announcements
AU  - Chakrabarty, Bidisha
AU  - Moulton, Pamela C.
AU  - Wang, Xu (Frank)
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 57
SP  - 100690
PY  - 2022
